lines.text:
[to Mrs. Wilson]
No matter how good I feel, Dennis has a cure for it.
Doesn't Margaret remind you of one of those pictures you're supposed to find 10 things wrong with?

[to Ruff, the dog]
When I get big, I'm going to build a house that doesn't have any corners.
I decided to send me to bed without any supper, since it's mostly vegetables.
Neato! Look at all these bones, what's this one called dad?
Alicesaurus, did you hear that mom? They named that one after you.
